

Application for making PC part requests

Used technologies:
- Java 1.8.0_221
- Spring framework 5.0.2.
- Hibernate 5.2.16.Final
- MySql 8.0
- Maven 3.6.1
- Tomcat 9.0
- Eclipse 2019-03 (4.11.0)

Database scripts provided in sql_scripts folder

Description of application:
Applicant is able to:
- make a new request;
- edit the existing one (if saved for later)

Additional functions to manager:
- view all requests
- view single request
- change request status (from submitted to completed)

Additional functions for admin:
- view all users
- view single user
- delete user